Pashov, B
Matamoros, Y
metadata.dc:description: In a sample of 23 breeding places of pacas (Agouti paca) in Costa Rica, the following parasites were found: Eimeria agoutii, Balantidium coli, Capillaria sp., Trichuris sp., Taenia sp., Strongyloides sp., and members of the superfamilies Strongyloidea and Ascaroidea.
metadata.dc:title: Parásitos intestinales del tepezcuinte, Agouti paca (Rodentia: Dasyproctidae) en Costa Rica.
[Intestinal parasites of Agouti paca (Rodentia: Dasyproctidae) in Costa Rica].
